article.description: — Darious Hall recorded 19 points and 16 rebounds to lift Central Arkansas to a 70-67 win over Oral Roberts on Saturday.
article.headline: Hall leads Central Arkansas over Oral Roberts 70-67
article.linkText: Hall leads Central Arkansas over Oral Roberts 70-67
article.story: CONWAY, Ark. -- — Darious Hall recorded 19 points and 16 rebounds to lift Central Arkansas to a 70-67 win over Oral Roberts on Saturday. Camren Hunter had 17 points and eight rebounds for Central Arkansas (1-3). Collin Cooper added 13 points. Issac McBride scored 25 points for the Golden Eagles (2-2). Trey Phipps added 10 points. Kareem Thompson had 10 points and eight rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
